README SliTaz forge
================================================================================


These repos provide all files, themes and custom packages used by the SliTaz 
network.


 * doc    : Use Dokuwiki
 * forum  : Use BBpress
 * scn    : Use Wordpress
 * people : Own php/html code
 * boot   : Own php/html code
 * bugs   : Own CGI/SHell code aka TazBug


To update or fix a theme, please test it well before committing and then 
notify <pankso at slitaz.org> who will update the modified theme.

To update or fix packages do the same as for the themes and then notify 
<erjo at slitaz.org>.


================================================================================
